# Playing Cards Computer

<catsoop-section>Introduction</catsoop-section>

We all share our feelings, needs, wills etc by talking to each other. Have you ever thought about how computers talk? We give it problems and it solves them very accurately. Do you wonder how? Computers understand the language of numbers which are known as **binary numbers**. To work on binary numbers computers need a circuit of **"Logic gates"**. Here we are going to build a logic gate with the help of playing cards. Let's see how these cards give us the result.

